A subset of WorldClim bioclimatic variables

Source: R/Worldclim_tmp.R
Worldclim_tmp.Rd

A subset of WorldClim bioclimatic variables cropped on the Central and Western Europe.

Usage

data(Worldclim_tmp)

Format

A data frame obtained from a SpatRaster with 1080 rows, 2160 columns, and 5 layers, namely: wc2.1_10m_bio_4, wc2.1_10m_bio_3, wc2.1_10m_bio_14, wc2.1_10m_bio_9, wc2.1_10m_bio_15.

Source

geodata::worldclim_global(var='bio', res=10, path=getwd())[[c(4, 3, 14, 9, 15)]]
